         If you're still level 33, I'd definitely look to buy some level 2 focus items.  They're much better than any other equipment you're going to get.  For example blackened alloy medallion is mana preservation 2, and can be had for a couple hundred plat.  It isn't a huge mana savings, but it does help more than the extra int you're getting from your neck now.</P><P>I'd also look into getting some more HP from your rings.  Either the Shadel Bandit Ring or Velium Fire Opal Rings.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
