        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         You should really look into getting focus items.  Those are the only things that are going to have a noticeable effect on your character.</P><P>Here's a link with a list :</P><P><a href="http://eq.crgaming.com/focus/" target="_blank">http://eq.crgaming.com/focus/</a></P><P>I'd get Extended Affliction II, Mana Preservation II, and Affliction Efficiency II items.  Affliction Haste II is also very nice.</P><P>Even something like a chipped bone bracelet which has affliction efficiency II and +wis is much better than PBB you have now.</P><P>Once you get those items, I'd looking into upgrading your HP thru rings or earrings as was mentioned above.</P><P>I evaluate items in following way :</P><P>Useful effect > HP/STA > Int/Mana > Resists > Strength</P><P>I still use a black alloy medallion as a 53 necro because it saves mana on root, beguile undead, dooming darkness, DMF, and invoke fear. I'd really like to get some of level 3 items, but they just aren't available on my server (stupid gem encrusted ring never dropped on my server).</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
