         To be honest, look into a Djarn's Amethyst ring, I used mine until recently when I got the Bone Ring of Condemnation off of Velk the Sorceror -- the Djarn's has 9 agi, 80 hp's and has Spell Haste II, great for all pre-50 spells.</P><P>Get a new robe, Froggies are cheap at least on my server, Tolapumj robes are also getting cheaper.</P><P>Get a Shadel Bandit ring, must have for you.</P><P>Items that are amazingly cheap right now and would be nice pieces for you are the Bloodweave gear from Tenebrous Mtns.  The gloves flat out own the ones you have, I've seen them for 500pp in Bazaar.  I take people (mainly guild friends) and slaughter the named Vampires and Coterie Generals - in 2 hours last trip had 2 pieces of Blood Weave gear drop and 5 General capes (thank god they aren't lore items).</P><P>Anyways, you aren't too badly equipped for your level -- and as in real life shop for bargains and take your time.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=139988" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=139988</a></P><P></P><P>Edited by - Aillar on 08/14/2002  11:24:15<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
